snippet: Authorities in San Diego County are searching for a missing woman with Alzheimer's disease who is the mother-in-law of Megadeth frontman Dave Mustaine....

headline.print_headline: Megadeth Singer's Mom-In-Law Missing in California
headline.main: Megadeth Singer's Mom-In-Law Missing in California

lead_paragraph: Authorities in San Diego County are searching for a missing woman with Alzheimer's disease who is the mother-in-law of Megadeth frontman Dave Mustaine.
